 <item> <title>U.S. Department of Education Reaches Settlement with South Carolina Department of Education on Funding for Children with Disabilities</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-department-education-reaches-settlement-south-carolina-department-education-funding-children-disabilities</link>
 <description>The  U.S. Department of Education (Department) announced today that it has reached  an agreement with the South Carolina Department of Education (SCDE), settling  the litigation involving the Department’s claim of South Carolina’s failure to  maintain state financial support for special education and related  services.</description>
